{"tid":2251556,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泛民戰勞顧會 斥建制出賣工人","createTime":"2020-10-21T01:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T01:30:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f754f4c5268a8b5e49a8ed2163c9b8b3ee44fa","tid":2251556,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:30:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/VVGPU6F4VZGNFKP476QNHN7QCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FVVGPU6F4VZGNFKP476QNHN7QCQ%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=d7616415\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FVVGPU6F4VZGNFKP476QNHN7QCQ%2F&h=efcad240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/VVGPU6F4VZGNFKP476QNHN7QCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n泛民戰勞顧會 斥建制出賣工人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vnw6KZltG04WporlpVnTWBGSWkQ=/3810x2540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TSVZ2AP4HBECPHT4EXNLPBIDIA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVnw6KZltG04WporlpVnTWBGSWkQ%3D%2F3810x2540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTSVZ2AP4HBECPHT4EXNLPBIDIA.JPG&h=8cf739ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■跨工會表示要破除壓迫工人不義制度，共同抗衡建制工會壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】勞工顧問委員會的勞方代表換屆選舉下月21日舉行，跨工會五名候選人昨日趁最後一日報名參選。候選人之一、社會及政治組織從業員工會理事李志宏表示，勞顧會的問題源於選舉制度不公，任由建制派長期把持，跨工會參選是為了凸顯制度問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轟選舉為建制度身訂做<br />\n<br />\n五名非建制派參選人分別為社會及政治組織從業員工會理事李志宏及。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他們指勞顧會問題源於選舉不公，全票制及一會一票選舉制度為建制工會度身訂做，形成勞方代表被建制派長期把持。李志宏坦言「我哋冇咩點考慮成功率，反而係諗點將抗爭帶去唔同層次」。他稱工會主張統一17天勞工假、訂立標準工時至44小時等，又特別關注爭取集體談判權、罷工權益等勞工議題。至於建制派方面，勞聯副主席譚金蓮及現屆勞方代表、工聯會鄧家彪早前已報名參選。"}]}